Text: RE documents for May conference callPlease find attached my comments on the documents that you sent to me yesterday Jack Jack Gibbons Chair Ontario Clean Air Alliance Church St Suite Toronto Ontario MY G Tel ext Fax Original Message From Yolanda Clegg mailto Sent Wednesday May PM To philip arvardedu Jack Gibbons Cc Yolanda Clegg Subject documents for May conference call Dear Advisory Board Member Thank you for your continued support of NACECs Initiative Environmental Challenges and Opportunities of the Evolving Continental Electricity Market Please find attached the following documents for your review and to be further discussed during the conference call Thursday May at EST an Interim Note for the Secretariat report a draft recommendations checklist for initial discussion a list of the advisory board members and bios please note that we have shortened some of the bios if you have yet to submit a bio please send a copy to Items to be discussed during conference call I Secretariat update progress expert report symposium II Process and approach for developing guidelinesrecommendations III Initial discussion of guidelinesrecommendations IV nd Advisory Board meeting date and venue Details of the conference call Participants from Canada and the United States should dial toll free Participants from Mexico should dial and ask the operator to charge this telephone call to the telephone number then enter the following Code If there is any problem with the communication during the call please dial Conference call reference C On behalf of my colleagues at NACEC Sincerely Yolanda Clegg Yolanda Clegg MSc Environment Economy and Trade Program North American Commission for Environmental Cooperation rue StJacques Ouest bureau Montreal Quebec CANADA HY N tel fax NACEC may doc
